caption: Everyone hates you at this subway, but I am easily satisfied by a tasty sandwich.

Extremely rude staff!!! I ordered a mobile order through the app and came to pick up my order. The older cashier yells at me saying they don’t participate in the mobile app deals only coupons and didn’t want to give me my drink even though I paid through the app already and was charged. I WILL NEVER GO THERE AGAIN EVER

Today is veterans Day and this chain is suppose to be offering free sandwiches! Veterans please stay away! Especially this store at Millennium station! Very Rude to Veterans! Didn't want to give the free sandwich! Had me stand and wait twenty minutes for owner to be rude! Didn't want to give the store # or cooperate # so could report how rude they where! They don't deserve our money or business when they treat a ten year Army Veteran or any one the way they treat me today! Just try to get a sandwich before I went to work, on this cold snowy day!

Well for starters I was told in the email I received upon acing an online order to go directly to the cash register when I arrived. I did that and politely told the older man working there my name & I was there to pick up my food. He yelled at me we have no mustard! So I replied, that's fine. When he showed me the receipt he said there's no tuna. I looked at knowing I double checked my order before placing it and saw tuna.. Along with everything else I ordered.  He yelled at me again nd said he has a long line (the customer next me even said that wasn't true) and I should have gotten in line. I told him I was picking up & was told to bypass the line in my email from Subway. So finally he starts to give the lady next to me her food and she told him, take care of her she needs to get back to work. (I was in uniform wearing a suit at that) I get my food FINALLY... Get back to work and the tuna is in fact there but on the wrong sandwich. And the one the tuna was suppose to be on didn't have no meat. I know this was long but I don't recommend anyone go here & I will certainly NEVER BE BACK!
i can say this place does it for me.

I understand that they don’t want random people just sitting in their restaurant without ordering anything, but mind you, me and three others had just barely sat down as soon as we entered and as I was preparing to head to the front to order, I overhear the older guy with glasses say “what are these people doing” in an angry tone, assuming we were just gonna sit in without ordering. He didn’t even notice me in the front for being too focused on my friends that were just sitting down. When he asked for my order, I told him “One second” and just left. That is not how you treat customers. They’re too money hungry to even care about quality service.

I have supported this Subway for awhile, they have poor customer service most of the time. I’m not sure if it’s my race or what. Sometimes in the morning they are a little friendly. That actually happened once.

Worst Subway ever!! I was 3rd in line and it took 18 minutes to make our sandwiches with 2 very old men running the sandwich line. The guy wrapped up my sandwich before I was even done with my order. Then they tell me they don't accept coupons from the app, and charged us for two 6 inch sandwiches rather than a foot long even though they were the same sandwich. I even had to ask for napkins since they didn't put any in the bag.
Very unfriendly owner/ manager. I haven’t been in months and now I remember why. Will not go back.

I just had the worst subway sandwich of my life. I wouldn’t recommend this subway. No wonder I was the only patron. Everyone else is aware of how horrible the food is. I guess you could say the one star is for the friendly staff.
Awful...I went back today after a long absence and now I know why I dont go to subway. Poor service and the bread is always stale.
Awesome show

Just walked in to the woman manager or owner screaming at the top of her lungs "you are a liar" over and over to an employee.  The staff out front were cringing and customers got up and left.  Worst employee/manager interaction I have ever witnessed.  I don't care what happened, you don't treat a human being that way.  I left and will never go back.  You should be ashamed of yourself.

(Translated by Google) Subway standard, fast, friendly and efficient service. Fresh food served in various bread combinations.  (Original) Padrão Subway, atendimento rápido, simpático e eficiente. Comida fresca servida nas várias combinações de pães.
Better than the average Subway

Customer Service is terrible! The most rude and racist establishment I've been to. I've never felt so uncomfortable at a restaurant ever. I will not be giving this place my hard earned money. Find another sandwich spot before you head to millennium station.

WORST SERVICE I'VE EVER ENCOUNTERED IN MY LIFE! MANAGER WAS INCREDIBLY RUDE TO MY DAUGHTER. I stopped there for a snack since I wasn't feeling well. The manager wouldn't allow my daughter to discard her Starbucks cup in his trash. Never in my life have I been treated so poorly. He ever stood there and stared at us until we left the premises. Disgusting!
Good location. Friendly stuff ☕
Food is great and the staff are incredibly generous!
Nice
Fresh food and good service.
Fresh tasting ingredients and overall great tasting food. The place is only hurt by the decor which is standard fast food fare. Great to eat at if yo're in town and need a quick fix
